      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 19 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 19 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>臨，元亨，利貞。至于八月有凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Lin (indicates that under the conditions supposed in it) there will be great progress and success, while it will be advantageous to be firmly correct. In the eighth month there will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
