      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 19 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 19 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：咸臨，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject advancing in company (with the subject of the second line). Through his firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
