      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 19 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：咸臨，吉无不利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject advancing in company (with the subject of the first line). There will be good fortune; (advancing) will be in every way advantageous.</seg>
      </tuv>
