      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：甘臨，无攸利。既憂之，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows one well pleased (indeed) to advance, (but whose action) will be in no way advantageous. If he become anxious about it (however), there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
